Their Green Tea Detox Mask 🍵🍃 is made with organic Matcha Green Tea, Lemongrass and Bentonite Clay that helps detoxifying your skin, remove impurities & unclog pores while replenishing your skin with real superfood nutrients. It’s 100% vegan & works on all skin types! I use it twice a week & leave it for about 20-30 minutes each time. 

Use code: LEYLA20 to save 20% OFF at TeamiBlends.com

node.text: If you guys are looking for a holy grail moisturizer, I finally found it! 🙌🏼 #teamipartner I used to never moisturize because I had acne-prone skin and it turns out I just needed good hydration to balance everything out. This formula is perfect because it's super lightweight but packed with superfood ingredients that are amazing for your skin! ✨I love that it's not greasy, oily or tacky which is super hard to come by. I love all the @teamiblends skincare and this is the perfect time to stock up, they are doing a special Black Friday deal for 50% off $100 by using code: LEYLA50 and after cyber Monday you can use LEYLA30 for 30% off! #thankyouteami

node.text: Ok guys, you asked for a tutorial on how I can possibly fit all my hair in a short wig like this.  Section your hair in two parts, wrap it around the head, secure with bobby pins and voila! No cap needed. They key is to lay your hair flat against the head so it’s not bumpy. Leave a 💗 if this video was helpful. Video by @rl_footage Stylist @arshin_7

node.title: How I fit all my hair in a wig! 🎥

node.text: #teamipartner I love hearing how much you guys are loving your Teami products (especially the MIXit 😉) It’s definitely my fav right now! 🤍 I wanted to share my latest smoothie obsession-the @teamiblends Butterfly Collagen (yes, I said butterfly 🙌🏼) you already know how I’m obsessed! 🦋🦋 It’s super unique because it’s made with butterfly flower, acai, and marine collagen! Loaded with antioxidants-I love that it gives me a boost of collagen to keep me looking & feeling my bes! The recipe I love making is oat milk, berries, a scoop of the butterfly collagen, and ice! Use my special discount: LEYLA20 for 20% off at checkout and let me know what you ordered! #thankyouteami
